options.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
options.result: AUSTIN,TX is the location with the highest weekly sales of $48,417.40
options.desc: The single store location with the most week to date revenue in dollars, representing top sales for this week.

options.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
options.result: AUSTIN,TX is the location with the highest MTD sales of $104,467.19

options.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
options.result: AUSTIN,TX is the location with the highest sales yesterday of $48,417.40
options.desc: The single store location with the daily revenue in dollars, representing top sales for yesterday.

options.query: SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;
options.result: The best selling product category is Knit Tops with 117,082 units sold.
options.desc: The best selling product category with the most units sold.

options.query: SELECT CONCAT('The total current inventory value is ', FORMAT(SUM([INVENTORY_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR];
options.result: The total current inventory value is $39,205,941.03
options.desc: The total dollar value of the current inventory.
